{"id":"f6ab8168251ac9b668cc645075f76249ca4483c3","url":"https://aiera.com.cn/2026/07/24/other/admin/105632/claude-agent%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e5%a4%a7%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0%ef%bc%81%e7%8b%82%e5%a1%9e500%e4%b8%aa%e6%8a%80%e8%83%bd%ef%bc%8c%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%8b%e7%9b%b4%e5%91%bc%e7%96%af%e7%8b%82","title":"Claude Agent突然大更新！狂塞500个技能，网友直呼疯狂 – 新智元","site_name":"新智元","source":"新智元","byline":null,"excerpt":"新智元报道","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n\t\t\t\n<h3>\n<section data-id=\"88402\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n<p><span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">&#160;&#160;</span></span></strong><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &#160;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</h3>\n<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n<p><span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_3b253ef414-204.png\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n</section>\n\n<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi3a2186z\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkt3w\"><span leaf=\"\">过去45天，Anthropic几乎没停过手。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk16dp\"><span textstyle=\"\">Fable 5和Mythos 5同时落地，Sonnet 5降价抢市场，Claude Code几乎日更。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkqds\"><span textstyle=\"\">昨天Cowork刚迭代完，今天Anthropic又在托管智能体平台（CMA）上一口气推出了六项更新：</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkztm\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">技能上限从20拉到500：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">一个会话装下整座企业知识库</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk19pz\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">思考力度五档调速</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">：简单路由省token，深度推理拉满</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk24sa\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">种子会话一步创建：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">直接带50条初始事件，冷启动归零</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkiyj\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">子agent实时流下探到线程级：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">每个子agent跑到哪、想到哪，实时可见</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkbv9\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">7种新webhook覆盖环境与记忆存储全生命周期：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">轮询可以退环境了</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1l25\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">agent更新版本字段变可选：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=ZjNiZGMzZjA0YzAwMjJhY2I2YjA3ZTAyMjQzYWQ0ODhfQVJObWRVdWtGa1V1SlJyWFJrZW5XOUlUdWs5Sk53SnVfVG9rZW46TkV6a2J0endab1dya0Z4cmRQYWNRbjh2bkdjXzE3ODQ3NzI1NDk6MTc4NDc3NjE0OV9WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505230826\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">单流程省掉版本管理开销</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1xcq\"><span textstyle=\"\">一个会话能挂500个技能、跑一整座企业知识库，Anthropic这是要给agent装操作系统啊！</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_52cf5b7cfb.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_c5af16aec8.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-200.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">技能上限暴涨到500</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">一个会话装下整个业务部门</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1ib9\"><span textstyle=\"\">CMA的技能（Skills）是给agent注入专业指令的知识包，之前上限只有20个。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkudl\"><span textstyle=\"\">然而，一个金融客服agent，光覆盖开户、KYC、反洗钱、投诉处理、合规免责、多语言切换就七八个了。再加上监管差异和AB测试版本，直接撞上天花板。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkgyl\"><span textstyle=\"\">现在这个数字直接拉到了500。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1wiu\"><span textstyle=\"\">这500个技能位由一个会话里的所有agent共享，跑在统一的托管沙盒里，agent之间共享内存和环境变量，由协调器统一调度——足以对应一个完整的业务单元。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk13xi\"><span textstyle=\"\">甚至，还可以直接把整套代码库规范、CI流水线配置、部署目标全塞进一个会话，让agent从写代码到上线一条龙全知道。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_cf371db6fc.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-200.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">思考力度五档调速</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">简单题不烧满血token</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkbjf\"><span textstyle=\"\">思考力度（effort）参数在API层面早就有了，但CMA里的agent以前不能单独设。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk2414\"><span textstyle=\"\">也就是说，整个session统一跑默认档位，问「今天几号」和「审计500页财报」用同一套深度。简单问题的过度推理，纯粹在烧token。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qke7\"><span textstyle=\"\">现在思考力度可以直接写进每个agent的模型配置里，五个档位：low / medium / high / xhigh / max。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk8pm\"><span textstyle=\"\">你跑一个多agent客服系统：分流coordinator用low，产品答疑用medium，投诉升级用high，法律合规用max。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk21lf\"><span textstyle=\"\">同一个session里，不同agent可以按任务难度跑在不同档位上。成本和质量之间，终于有了一个连续的旋钮。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_5509774bba.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-200.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">冷启动归零</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">子agent黑盒也拆了</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkavn\"><span textstyle=\"\">创建CMA会话以前要两步：先POST一个空壳，再逐条塞初始事件。高并发场景下，往返延迟一层层叠上去，冷启动拖得很慢。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1oyl\"><span textstyle=\"\">现在一步到位。POST /v1/sessions 直接带initial_events，最多50条初始事件，会话生下来就知道自己要干什么。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1jrg\"><span textstyle=\"\">同一批更新里，agent更新接口的version字段也变成了可选。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1o80\"><span textstyle=\"\">以前每次更新都得传版本号做并发控制，版本不匹配直接返回409错误。现在单流程场景可以直接省掉这一步。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkk2e\"><span textstyle=\"\">子agent的可观测性也迈了一大步。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qks1t\"><span textstyle=\"\">6月底CMA刚上线会话级的event_deltas，能实时预览主agent的文本输出。但子agent还是黑盒，不管是跑偏了，还是卡死了，只能得等超时才知道。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk2oz\"><span textstyle=\"\">这次直接下探到线程级。订阅子agent的独立线程流，想到哪里、写到哪里，实时看得见。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_650ddbf096.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_fe2b3a5668.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-200.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">7种新webhook补位</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">轮询时代结束了</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qktty\"><span textstyle=\"\">CMA在6月底已经上线了agent和部署生命周期的webhook。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1648\"><span textstyle=\"\">这次补上了剩下的两大块：4种环境事件 + 3种记忆存储事件。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkbx0\"><span textstyle=\"\">至此，CMA的整个生命周期——环境搭建、agent部署、运行状态、记忆管理，全部可以事件驱动地跟外部系统打通。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk18zb\"><span textstyle=\"\">环境暂停时自动触发告警，记忆存储更新时同步到自家数据库，新环境创建时自动挂上监控。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1gn\"><span textstyle=\"\">从「API产品」到「可运维平台」，这是最后一块拼图。</span></span></p>\n\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-200.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic赌的是OS级深度</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1l2d\"><span textstyle=\"\">走到2026年7月，AI agent基础设施竞赛已经进入到了深水区，更新频率几乎要按天计算。</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk20ks\"><span textstyle=\"\">OpenAI赌入口。</span>把聊天、编程、自主工作全塞进一个ChatGPT超级应用，用最大用户基数锁住开发者。</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qky9r\"><span textstyle=\"\">Google赌基础设施。GCP + TPU + 协议标准，底层建护城河。</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk12sf\"><span textstyle=\"\">Anthropic赌OS级深度。托管沙盒 + 全栈agent控制 + 思考力度调速，在单agent的能力密度上做文章。</span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qk1gz6\"><span textstyle=\"\">从20到500，Anthropic盘算的是，什么时候能把agent变成和操作系统一样基础的东西。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mrwvi9qkwlx\"><span textstyle=\"\">速度已经给出了答案：很快。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/ClaudeDevs/status/2080009523952263295?s=20</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">编辑：摩西</span></span></p>\n\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">秒追ASI</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">⭐</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">点赞、转发、在看一键三连</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">⭐</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">点亮星标，锁定新智元极速推送！</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_4d80689a0a-205.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_50d0834dc7-37.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n\n\t\t</div></DIV>","content_text":"新智元报道 过去45天，Anthropic几乎没停过手。 Fable 5和Mythos 5同时落地，Sonnet 5降价抢市场，Claude Code几乎日更。 昨天Cowork刚迭代完，今天Anthropic又在托管智能体平台（CMA）上一口气推出了六项更新： 技能上限从20拉到500：一个会话装下整座企业知识库 思考力度五档调速：简单路由省token，深度推理拉满 种子会话一步创建：直接带50条初始事件，冷启动归零 子agent实时流下探到线程级：每个子agent跑到哪、想到哪，实时可见 7种新webhook覆盖环境与记忆存储全生命周期：轮询可以退环境了 agent更新版本字段变可选：单流程省掉版本管理开销 一个会话能挂500个技能、跑一整座企业知识库，Anthropic这是要给agent装操作系统啊！ 技能上限暴涨到500 一个会话装下整个业务部门 CMA的技能（Skills）是给agent注入专业指令的知识包，之前上限只有20个。 然而，一个金融客服agent，光覆盖开户、KYC、反洗钱、投诉处理、合规免责、多语言切换就七八个了。再加上监管差异和AB测试版本，直接撞上天花板。 现在这个数字直接拉到了500。 这500个技能位由一个会话里的所有agent共享，跑在统一的托管沙盒里，agent之间共享内存和环境变量，由协调器统一调度——足以对应一个完整的业务单元。 甚至，还可以直接把整套代码库规范、CI流水线配置、部署目标全塞进一个会话，让agent从写代码到上线一条龙全知道。 思考力度五档调速 简单题不烧满血token 思考力度（effort）参数在API层面早就有了，但CMA里的agent以前不能单独设。 也就是说，整个session统一跑默认档位，问「今天几号」和「审计500页财报」用同一套深度。简单问题的过度推理，纯粹在烧token。 现在思考力度可以直接写进每个agent的模型配置里，五个档位：low / medium / high / xhigh / max。 你跑一个多agent客服系统：分流coordinator用low，产品答疑用medium，投诉升级用high，法律合规用max。 同一个session里，不同agent可以按任务难度跑在不同档位上。成本和质量之间，终于有了一个连续的旋钮。 冷启动归零 子agent黑盒也拆了 创建CMA会话以前要两步：先POST一个空壳，再逐条塞初始事件。高并发场景下，往返延迟一层层叠上去，冷启动拖得很慢。 现在一步到位。POST /v1/sessions 直接带initial_events，最多50条初始事件，会话生下来就知道自己要干什么。 同一批更新里，agent更新接口的version字段也变成了可选。 以前每次更新都得传版本号做并发控制，版本不匹配直接返回409错误。现在单流程场景可以直接省掉这一步。 子agent的可观测性也迈了一大步。 6月底CMA刚上线会话级的event_deltas，能实时预览主agent的文本输出。但子agent还是黑盒，不管是跑偏了，还是卡死了，只能得等超时才知道。 这次直接下探到线程级。订阅子agent的独立线程流，想到哪里、写到哪里，实时看得见。 7种新webhook补位 轮询时代结束了 CMA在6月底已经上线了agent和部署生命周期的webhook。 这次补上了剩下的两大块：4种环境事件 + 3种记忆存储事件。 至此，CMA的整个生命周期——环境搭建、agent部署、运行状态、记忆管理，全部可以事件驱动地跟外部系统打通。 环境暂停时自动触发告警，记忆存储更新时同步到自家数据库，新环境创建时自动挂上监控。 从「API产品」到「可运维平台」，这是最后一块拼图。 Anthropic赌的是OS级深度 走到2026年7月，AI agent基础设施竞赛已经进入到了深水区，更新频率几乎要按天计算。 OpenAI赌入口。把聊天、编程、自主工作全塞进一个ChatGPT超级应用，用最大用户基数锁住开发者。 Google赌基础设施。GCP + TPU + 协议标准，底层建护城河。 Anthropic赌OS级深度。托管沙盒 + 全栈agent控制 + 思考力度调速，在单agent的能力密度上做文章。 从20到500，Anthropic盘算的是，什么时候能把agent变成和操作系统一样基础的东西。 速度已经给出了答案：很快。 参考资料： https://x.com/ClaudeDevs/status/2080009523952263295?s=20 编辑：摩西 秒追ASI ⭐点赞、转发、在看一键三连⭐ 点亮星标，锁定新智元极速推送！","fetched_at":"2026-07-24T14:38:18.592Z","ok":true}